2,612 SF Symbols

SF Symbols is the system icon framework in iOS 13+. This site lists all the names of available icons.
Please note that no icons are displayed on this site due to license restrictions. To view the icon images, you'll need to download the SF Symbols Mac app from this page.
This site will always be open source and ad-free. If you'd like to support this project and others like it, please download CIFilter.io.
